Handles login procedures for all types of users in the Hospital Management System.
MainApp
The entry point for the Healthcare Management System (HMS).
MedicalRecord
Represents a medical record associated with an appointment within the healthcare management system.
MedicalRecordManager
Manages the loading, saving, and manipulation of medical records within the hospital management system.
Medication
Represents a medication with its name, stock levels, and thresholds for low stock alerts.
MedicineManager
Handles the management of medications, including loading from, saving to, and updating the medication inventory in a CSV file.
NumericValidator
A validator that checks if a given input string is purely numeric.
Patient
Represents a patient in the hospital management system, extending the User class with specific attributes for a patient's medical and personal information.
PatientAppointmentScheduler
This class provides functionalities for patients to manage their appointments, including viewing available slots, scheduling new appointments, cancelling or rescheduling existing ones, and viewing past medical records.
PatientAppointmentViewer
This class provides functionalities for patients to view their appointments, including viewing available slots, past appointments and viewing past medical records.
PatientCreator
Facilitates the creation of new patient accounts within the hospital management system.
PatientManager
Manages patient data, including loading from and saving to a CSV file, and validating patient login details.
PatientMenu
Represents a menu interface for patients to interact with various functionalities related to their medical records, appointments, and personal information.
Pharmacist
Represents a pharmacist, a staff member responsible for managing medications and prescriptions.
PharmacistController
 
PharmacistMenu
A menu for pharmacists to interact with and perform various tasks related to pharmacy management.
Prescription
Represents a prescription associated with a medical appointment.
ReplenishManager
Manages replenishment requests for medications, including loading, saving, and updating requests.
ReplenishmentRequest
Represents a request for replenishment of a specific medication.
SelectionMenu
Provides a user interface for selecting between login and patient account creation options.
Staff
Represents a generic staff member in the hospital management system.

Manages staff operations such as loading, saving, and validating staff login credentials.

Represents a common interface for staff menus in the hospital management system.
